com.badlogic.gdx.graphics

Interface GL10

  • All Superinterfaces:
    GLCommon
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    GL11

    public interface GL10
extends GLCommon
    Interface wrapping all standard OpenGL ES 1.0 methods. Note that this excludes any fixed point OpenGL ES 1.0 methods!
    Author:
    mzechner
